    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"246273\">@Bhavik Mehta</span>, would you be able to translate <a href=\"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib3/blob/irrational-pi/src/analysis/special_functions/trigonometric/pi.lean\">https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib3/blob/irrational-pi/src/analysis/special_functions/trigonometric/pi.lean</a> and PR it?</p>",
