    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110038\">@Kevin Buzzard</span> we have completed the proof of the irrationality of <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>ζ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>3</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\zeta(3)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07378em;\">ζ</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">3</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> in Lean! We'll adjust our proof to show <span class=\"katex\"><span class=\"katex-mathml\"><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><semantics><mrow><mi>ζ</mi><mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo><mn>2</mn><mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo></mrow><annotation encoding=\"application/x-tex\">\\zeta(2)</annotation></semantics></math></span><span class=\"katex-html\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><span class=\"base\"><span class=\"strut\" style=\"height:1em;vertical-align:-0.25em;\"></span><span class=\"mord mathnormal\" style=\"margin-right:0.07378em;\">ζ</span><span class=\"mopen\">(</span><span class=\"mord\">2</span><span class=\"mclose\">)</span></span></span></span> is irrational!</p>",
        "id": 478674074,
        "sender_full_name": "Junqi Liu",
        "timestamp": 1729762689
    },
